This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and text summarization. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves machine learning techniques. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves training a model to generate summaries. It could also be classified under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it involves retrieving relevant parts of the source document. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves the use of neural networks for text summarization.
